    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >部署与进攻！</h2>50个巨型首领占领了美国的50个城市（包括最近被吞并的蒙特利尔）。你的任务是穿越整个国家，集结部队解救恐惧的人民。从一群只有希望的平民和士兵开始训练他们：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/5fd93817c841e2abf80304a11e621b2d.poster.avif?t=1719334893\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/5fd93817c841e2abf80304a11e621b2d.webm?t=1719334893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/5fd93817c841e2abf80304a11e621b2d.mp4?t=1719334893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招募你的民兵</h2>你会选择将你的公民变成坚强的部队的士兵，还是将他们变成吸取力量的吸血鬼的魅魔？如果你涉足邪术，带上一位牧师来引导你的亡灵的力量。被尼亚拉托提普逼到绝境了吗？部署一枚战术核弹，将你的民兵的攻击集中在一个巨大的爆炸中。当然，这会将他们变成放射性废料，但这就是你得到突变体的方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/3afd8579353cb1e876b5799052e9044e.poster.avif?t=1719334893\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/3afd8579353cb1e876b5799052e9044e.webm?t=1719334893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/3afd8579353cb1e876b5799052e9044e.mp4?t=1719334893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >破坏游戏平衡的协同效应！</h2>一旦进入战场，你的25名部队将随机部署。你无法控制他们的位置，这意味着你的民兵的组成最为重要。每个部队都有自己的优势和劣势，但最重要的是协同效应。招募合适的部队组合，你很可能能够击败巨型首领。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/2ea8bc27cda3ec41b7554b7a3083531e.poster.avif?t=1719334893\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/2ea8bc27cda3ec41b7554b7a3083531e.webm?t=1719334893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358770/extras/2ea8bc27cda3ec41b7554b7a3083531e.mp4?t=1719334893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
